Correlações

datasaurus_dozen %>% 
  group_by(dataset) %>% 
  summarise(correlacao = cor(x, y))

Boxplots

datasaurus_dozen %>% 
  group_by(dataset) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = dataset, y = y)) + 
  geom_boxplot()

ggplot(datasaurus_dozen, aes(x=x, y=y, colour=dataset))+
  geom_point()+
  # theme_void()+
  theme(legend.position = "none")+
  facet_wrap(~dataset, ncol=3)
